# ── Firebase Admin Credentials ──────────────────────────────────────
# The scraper supports three methods (checked in order):
#
# Method 1: Service account JSON file
#   Place a file named "serviceAccountKey.json" in this directory.
#
# Method 2: Full JSON string (matches existing Bangis scraper pattern)
#   FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT='{"type":"service_account","project_id":"...","private_key":"...","client_email":"..."}'
#
# Method 3: Individual environment variables
#   FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=bangis-dda48
#   FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=firebase-adminsdk-fbsvc@bangis-dda48.iam.gserviceaccount.com
#   FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
